Package: EconoTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Economic Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alen K Suresh
Maintainer: Alen K Suresh <alenkarakkattil4444@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of tools to fetch, process, and visualize
    common economic indicators from public APIs like the Federal Reserve
    Economic Data (FRED). Includes functions for calculating moving averages
    and an interactive Shiny application for data exploration.
